(secondQuint)A Pilot Study of TRV130 for the Treatment of Fracture Pain.

 This study is designed to evaluate the analgesic efficacy of TRV130 for the treatment of moderate to severe acute pain associated with a long bone fracture in patients presenting to the ED.

 The safety and tolerability of TRV130 will also be evaluated in this open-label pilot study.

